WordPress core editor styles (reference only)

The following directories are part of WordPress core and are indexed only so the agent can inspect Gutenberg and admin UI styles when implementing custom dashboard styling or dark mode:

- wp-admin/css
- wp-includes/css/dist
- wp-includes/blocks

These folders belong to WordPress core and must never be modified.

They are included in the index for reference purposes only.

All styling changes must be implemented in the project's custom codebase, primarily in:

wp-content/themes/vantagepictures-child
or approved custom plugins within:
wp-content/plugins/
